snippet.textDisplay:
Raat ko jab bhi, main akela hoon,
Dil ke andar bas tera jahan hoon.
Yaadon ka dariya, beh jaata hai,
Tera chehra hi mera aasra hai.


2. Chorus
Tera naam, main khamoshi mein pukaarun,
Tere bina main adhoora sa lagun.
Har geet mein, bas tujhko hi utaarun,
Tere bina main adhoora sa lagun.


3. Verse 2
Sapno mein tu aake keh jaata hai,
“Main hoon tere saath, tu bas gaa zara.”
Par subah hote hi, sab mita jaata,
Meri rooh tujhko hi dhoondhta.


4. Chorus (Repeat)
Tera naam, main khamoshi mein pukaarun,
Tere bina main adhoora sa lagun.
Har geet mein, bas tujhko hi utaarun,
Tere bina main adhoora sa lagun.


5. Outro
Dil ki dhadkan mein tu bas gaya hai,
Mera har lafz tujhse juda hai.


Written by me ANUV bhai plz sing this song once This song is for your dad plz sing this once  hope you  like his song ❤️
